From fdf0ca19ebf5f8b3d06fef0a47ea45a36ac62a54 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ekane bryan <ekanebryan5@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 01:33:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(ux): table view toggle, real money figures, mobile
 polish
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Table: user-controlled Table/Grid view toggle (default per device,
  remembered in localStorage) — works on any screen size.
- Wallet & Payouts: show real figures via formatMoney (no more 'Free'
  for 0 balances/amounts).
- Organizer/admin mobile nav: remove duplicate 'Settings' link.
- Event details: show the registration deadline in the info grid.
- My registrations: horizontal swipe carousel on mobile, grid on desktop.
- Ticket page: smaller responsive text sizes so it fits without scrolling.
- Notifications: 2-col grid on desktop / 1-col on mobile + Read more/less
  for long messages.
- EN/FR keys: events.details.deadlineLabel, notifications.readMore/showLess.
